Package: ComptoxR
Title: Wrappers and Functions for Accessing USEPA CompTox Chemical
    Dashboard and Other Products
Version: 1.5.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Sean", "Thimons",
    email = "thimons.sean@epa.gov",
    role = c("aut", "cre")
    )
Description: Provides access to the US EPA's CompTox Chemical Dashboard APIs
    and related products for chemical risk screening and prioritization. The
    package enables chemical identification and search through multiple
    identifier types (DTXSID, CAS, SMILES, InChI, names), hazard and safety
    assessment (including GHS codes, NFPA safety information, cancer,
    genotoxicity data), bioactivity and toxicity screening from multiple
    databases (GenRA, TEST, ECOTOX, ToxValDB), chemical properties and molecular
    descriptors, environmental fate and exposure data, and risk prioritization
    with regulatory list associations. It supports batch processing for large
    queries and integrates data from CompTox Chemistry Dashboard, GenRA Engine,
    Toxicity Estimation Software Tool (TEST), ECOTOX, ToxValDB, and EPI Suite.
URL: https://github.com/seanthimons/ComptoxR
BugReports: https://github.com/seanthimons/ComptoxR/issues
